00:40:01,858 --> 00:40:02,984
Bunuh saja aku.

381
00:40:06,446 --> 00:40:07,447
Kumohon…

382
00:40:11,493 --> 00:40:12,911
bunuh aku.

383
00:40:20,001 --> 00:40:21,002
Chan-hyeok.

384
00:41:43,460 --> 00:41:46,046
Berapa lama lagi
kau akan terus menyendiri di sini?

385
00:41:49,216 --> 00:41:50,842
Kau adalah pelindung,

386
00:41:50,926 --> 00:41:54,221
