00:45:10,542 --> 00:45:11,543
Tolong bantu

431
00:45:13,128 --> 00:45:14,129
kakakku.

432
00:45:15,922 --> 00:45:17,674
Hanya kau yang bisa menyelamatkannya.

433
00:45:18,049 --> 00:45:19,300
Apa maksudmu?

434
00:45:20,718 --> 00:45:21,719
Kakakku…

435
00:45:24,597 --> 00:45:26,057
